omni-dev atlassian jira - JIRA issue management, search, agile boards, and more

JIRA issue management, search, agile boards, and more

Usage: jira <COMMAND>

Commands:
  read        Fetches a JIRA issue and outputs it as JFM markdown or ADF JSON
